{"lemma":"سَبْقُ","slug":"سَبْقُ","root":"س.ب.ق","root_slug":"س-ب-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ب-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَبْق","root":"سبق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18785","n18789","n18790"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to precede, to come before (something or someone)","examples":[{"text":"يَلِي ٱلْعَدَدَ ٢ ٱلْعَدَدُ ٣ وَيَسْبِقُهُ ٱلْعَدَدُ ١.","english":"The number 2 is followed by the number 3 and preceded by the number 1."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَبَقَ (sabaqa) (form I), anticipation","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"],"examples":[{"text":"سَبْق الإصْرَار","english":"premeditation"},{"text":"سَبْق صِحَافِيّ","english":"breaking news, sensational news"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"plural of سَابِق (sābiq)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18785","headword_ar":"سبّق","root":"sbq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tasobiyqN","text_ar":"تَسْبِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"received, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stake,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager, laid at a race"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a shooting-match, to be taken by the successful competitor"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IAar, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aqotuhu","text_ar":"سَبَّقْتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"received, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, Mgh, Msb.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aqotuhu","text_ar":"سَبَّقْتُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I gave him the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Az, Mgh, Msb.) Thus it has two contr. significations. (IAar, Az, Mgh, O, Msb, K.) Hence, in the trad. of Rukáneh the wrestler,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA tusab~iquniY","text_ar":"مَا تُسَبِّقُنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What wilt thou give me"},{"kind":"text","text":"[if I overcome] ? and he said, The third of my sheep, or goats. (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aqa","text_ar":"سَبَّقَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albadorapa bayona Al$~uEaraA='i","text_ar":"البَدْرَةَ بَيْنَ الشُّعَرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sum of money termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bdrp","text_ar":"بدرة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stake,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among the poets,"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be taken by him who should overcome. (Z, TA.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amara biA_ijoraA='i Alxayoli wasb~aqahaA valaAvapa A^aEo*uqK mino valaAvi","text_ar":"اَمَرَ بِاـِجْرَا=ءِ الخَيْلِ وَسبَّقَهَا ثَلَاثَةَ اَعْذُقٍ مِنْ ثَلَاثِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naxalaAtK","text_ar":"نَخَلَاتٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ordered the making of the horse to run, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave them as a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three racemes of dates from three palm-trees"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or it may mean,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"received, as their"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":": or it [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sbqhA","text_ar":"سبقها"},{"kind":"text","text":"] may be without teshdeed, [as a subst. with its affixed pronoun,] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the property assigned"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as their"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L, TA.) ―         -b3-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aqotu bayona Alxayoli","text_ar":"سَبَّقْتُ بَيْنَ الخَيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I gave a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaq","text_ar":"سَبَق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among the horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aqotu","text_ar":"سَبَّقْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxayola","text_ar":"الخَيْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahaA","text_ar":"بَيْنَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sAbqt","text_ar":"سابقت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sent forth the horses with their riders upon them, to see which of them would outstrip."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sb~qt Al$~aApu","text_ar":"سبّقت الشَّاةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ewe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she-goat, cast her young one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fœtus, in an incomplete state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sb~gt","text_ar":"سبّغت"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"g","text_ar":"غ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is better known. (Ibn-'Abbád, O.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sab~aqotu","text_ar":"سَبَّقْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~aAy^ira","text_ar":"الطَّايِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I put the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sibaAqaAni","text_ar":"سِبَاقَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pair of jesses"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the legs of the bird, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shackled it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["IAar","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n18789","headword_ar":"سِبْقٌ","root":"sbq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A competitor"},{"kind":"text","text":"of another"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in striving to precede, to be before"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ahead, to outgo"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"outstrip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to have precedence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asobaAqN","text_ar":"اَسْبَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the sing. is also used as a pl.:] you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo siboqiY","text_ar":"هُمْ سِبْقِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asobaAqiY","text_ar":"اَسْبَاقِى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humaA siboqaAni","text_ar":"هُمَا سِبْقَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are two that compete"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (El-Moheet, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["L"]},{"entry_id":"n18790","headword_ar":"سَبَقٌ","root":"sbq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stake,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager, that is laid between the persons concerned in a race,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, O, Mgh, * Msb, * K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a shooting-match; in the former case taken by"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the owner of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the one that outstrips;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suboqapN","text_ar":"سُبْقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (K:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asobaAqN","text_ar":"اَسْبَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA sabaqa A_il~aA fiY xuf~K A^awo HaAfirK A^awo naSolK","text_ar":"لَا سَبَقَ اـِلَّا فِى خُفٍّ اَوْ حَافِرٍ اَوْ نَصْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall be no stake,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wager, except in the case of"},{"kind":"text","text":"the racing of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels, or of horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mules"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"asses, or in the case of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the arrowhead"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lance-head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] shooting or casting [the lance]: for all these affairs are preparations for engaging in fight with the enemy; and mules and asses are included because they carry the baggage of the army. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lesson"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a boy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is learned each day in the school;"},{"kind":"text","text":"also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imaAmN","text_ar":"اـِمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Am","text_ar":"ام"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["T","TA","K"]}]}}